text: Lene Pedersen (born 22 April 1972) is a Danish rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:Danish female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Denmark Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
